title: TUESDAY 2/9 - Super Bowl hangover
itunes:title: TUESDAY 2/9 - Super Bowl hangover
description:
The Buccaneers still soaking in the Super Bowl win as Tom Brady had his MVP press conference where he talked about the joy of winning a championship with new teammates (0:42). Speaking of Brady, Head Coach Bruce Arians talked about adding that missing piece to the locker room (1:24). As for Patrick Mahomes, he reflected back on his Super Bowl performance (2:26). Plus, we run down the latest coaching moves from the NFC North
